OL,3,CMother's rare and dangerous cancer was
OL,4,Cmistaken for a verruca by doctors
OL,6,FA mum of twins has described how she
OL,7,Fsurvived a rare and aggressive form of
OL,8,Fskin cancer which was initially
OL,9,Fdismissed as a verruca.
OL,11,FBeatrice Buckley developed a mole on
OL,12,Fher foot while pregnant with her twin
OL,13,Fsons Alfred and Thomas.
OL,15,FShe said: "I fell pregnant in 2020,
OL,16,Fand in the really early stages of my
OL,17,Fpregnancy, I noticed a little dark
OL,18,Fspot, so bigger than a freckle.
