OL,6,FIn a matter of months, the skin lesion
OL,7,Fgrew to the size of a 10 pence coin.
OL,8,FThe 39-year-old added: "When the twins
OL,9,Fwere about eight months old it had
OL,10,Fgrown in size.
OL,12,F"It started doing all of the things
OL,13,Fthat you are supposed to look out for,
OL,14,Fit had doubled in size, it was
OL,15,Fbleeding, when I went running it was
OL,16,Firritated.
