OL,3,CMother's rare and dangerous cancer was
OL,4,Cmistaken for a verruca by doctors
OL,6,F"So I went to the GP thinking 'this
OL,7,Fcould be nasty' but even the GP
OL,8,Fthought it was a verruca which had
OL,9,Fprobably just rubbed in my running
OL,10,Fshoes. They only referred me to
OL,11,Fdermatology because of my skin type."
OL,13,FEven dermatologists did not think the
OL,14,Fmole was anything sinister until tests
OL,15,Frevealed that it was a rare and
OL,16,Fpotentially fatal form of cancer,
OL,17,Fstage three acral melanoma, the
OL,18,Fdisease which led to the death of
OL,19,FReggae artist Bob Marley in 1981 aged
OL,20,Fjust 36.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@eO]
