OL,3,CMother's rare and dangerous cancer was
OL,4,Cmistaken for a verruca by doctors
OL,6,FAccording to Cancer Research UK, only
OL,7,F1% to 3% of melanoma cases are acral
OL,8,Fmelanoma, a rare type of skin cancer
OL,9,Fwhich is usually found on the palms of
OL,10,Fthe hands, the soles of the feet, or
OL,11,Funder the nails.
OL,13,FThis type of cancer is more common
OL,14,Famong people with brown or black skin,
OL,15,Fmiddle aged and older adults.
OL,17,FMs Buckley said: "It's terrifying. The
OL,18,Fword cancer is incredibly scary. When
OL,19,Fyou hear the word cancer, your mind
OL,20,Fimmediately goes to the worst place.
