OL,6,F"You do have thoughts in the middle of
OL,7,Fthe night of your children growing up
OL,8,Fwithout a mum, and it's awful."
OL,10,FDoctors found that the cancer had
OL,11,Fspread to a number of lymph nodes.
OL,13,FBut after three surgeries and targeted
OL,14,Ftherapy, Ms Buckley is now disease-
OL,15,Ffree and helping with the National
OL,16,FInstitute for Health and Care Research
OL,17,F(NIHR) Be Part of Research project
OL,18,FMyMelanoma.
