OL,6,F"For me, I was able to take two
OL,7,Ftablets twice a day from home, it
OL,8,Fwasn't a picnic, I was quite unwell
OL,9,Flast year, but nevertheless, now six
OL,10,Fmonths on from finishing my treatment,
OL,11,FI'm here.
OL,13,F"I don't have any residual side
OL,14,Feffects; I am well and I am cancer
OL,15,Ffree. I feel so grateful to research
OL,16,Ffor having brought these drugs to the
OL,17,Fmarket."
